.SH REGISTERS
.sp
.LP
Formatting distances can be controlled in \fB-mm\fR by means of built-in number
registers. For example, this sets the line length to 6.5 inches:
.sp
.in +2
.nf
\&.nr  LL  6.5i
.fi
.in -2

.sp
